#

Rich Tomato and Herb Meat Sauce with Grilled Pork Cutlets

$25
650 kcal
Difficulty: 60%

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Tags:

PorkBeefItalianComfort Food

Description

Savor the robust flavors of a rich tomato and herb meat sauce, perfectly paired with juicy grilled pork cutlets for a satisfying meal.

Ingredients

  • Pork cutlets: 4 pieces
  • Ground beef: 1 pound
  • Canned crushed tomatoes: 28 ounces
  • Onion: 1 large, diced
  • Garlic: 4 cloves, minced
  • Italian seasoning: 2 teaspoons
  • Fresh basil: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • Olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
  • Parmesan cheese: 1/2 cup, grated
